data.description: DON'T MISS THIS stunning home on lg corner lot offering 4 bds, 2.5 bths, & dedicated office offering ample living space. Bright living area w/Ash hdw floors, gourmet kitchen w/SS appliances & granite counters. P-suite features lux soaking tub & walk-in closet. Landscaped yard w/org fruit trees, hot tub, & covered patio creates a tranquil retreat. 3-car garage w/electrical upgrades suits hobbyists, plus RV space w/plug & 220v. Desirable neighborhood near Kingsborough Park w/convenient access to amenities. Nestled in the charming neighborhood of Dallas, Oregon, 273 SW Bell Dr. offers an exceptional blend of comfort and functionality. This immaculate residence boasts four bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, and dedicated office, providing ample space for all your needs. As you step inside this quality built home, you're greeted by a spacious living area filled with natural light due to the large number of fully wrapped windows, ash hardwood floors, and custom touches creating a warm and inviting atmosphere, while the office provides a dedicated space for work or study. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and plenty of cabinet space.The primary suite is a vibrant retreat, featuring a luxurious soaking tub in the ensuite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closet. Additional bedrooms offer comfort and privacy. The fourth bedroom has storage closet & currently be used as bonus room, presenting endless possibilities.Outside, the meticulously landscaped yard showcases organic fruit trees, raised beds, and ornamentals, perfect for gardening enthusiasts. A relaxing hot tub awaits you on the spacious patio, offering a peaceful oasis to unwind and recharge.This spacious property boasts a 3-car garage, RV space with plugin, and an exterior 220v junction box, catering to diverse lifestyle needs. The garage/shop features electrical upgrades, wired for plasma cutter/welder, and equipped with air compressor lines, ideal for hobbyists or DIY enthusiasts.Located on a large corner lot, this home offers privacy and tranquility while still being just a block away from Kingsborough Park. Enjoy easy access to schools, shopping, dining, and entertainment options, as well as convenient commuting with nearby highways. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property your own!For inquiries or to schedule a private showing, please contact:Tiffany BouchardHomeSmart Realty Grouptiffanyb.realty@gmail.com503-871-5929
